text: Tashi Peljor is a archer from Bhutan. Peljor competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics and 2008 Summer Olympics.Tashi PELJOR He was born on 15 July 1978.Tashi Peljor == References == Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Bhutanese archers Category:Olympians for Bhutan
